OL,5, Retail consultant Mary Portas has      
OL,6, written an open letter to John Lewis   
OL,7, warning that the department store had  
OL,8, "let go" of its soul.                  
OL,10,FThe brand expert described the UK      
OL,11,Fretail giant as part of "our collective
OL,12,Fcultural identity".                    
OL,14,FHer comments come after John Lewis     
OL,15,Frevealed it was considering a change to
OL,16,Fits employee-owned business structure, 
OL,17,Fso altering decades of tradition.      
OL,19,FChair Sharon White said she wanted the 
OL,20,Fbrand to thrive for generations.       
